The zoom h2 quality is good too from what i&#39;ve heard from kristins files also.  The rt-evp is tiny and is good for both evp and ghost box recordings.

The cheaper the quality, the better for regular evp i&#39;ve found.  But for recording box sessions, you have to get something good.  That way others can hear them clearly.  

Also, a cheap recording gets worse when run through an audio editor.

S-H



